Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:10.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus has come for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:16.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is the Master's grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Related to Makarov, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this guy totally \Nwiped the floor with all of ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Came to visit the founder's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:25.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be in Fairy Tail, if you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:33.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to visit Mavis's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:37.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And looky what I found... \NThe 2nd master's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:43.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're here and all, maybe \NI'll make you a grave, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Man Without the Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:54.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Honestly, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never thought the boy would have \Nsuch a stuck-up grandkid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You move fairly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that magic power, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the boy had someone other \Nthan Gildarts at this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man once told me that \Nwhen facing a strong opponent:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:46.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"It don't matter how strong the guy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more important \Nis standing up to him."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that right, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:52.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like the excuse of a weakling to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had a chance to warm up, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come at me, youngster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:20.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's even a small gap in the \Ndefensive runes, they lose all purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crucial they are precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to check the fine \Ndetails as you fill them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:26.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll protect you, Gajeel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have something to say, \Nthen say it loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:38.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should really lie \Ndown again, Elf-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've rested plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could at least stand watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were crying out in \Nyour sleep, Elf-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eva! Eva!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you guys are sure takin' it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And where the hell were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got rid of the glasses guy \Nwho was out for the count.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:11.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he had some kind of Body Link, \Nhe'd have given away our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will proceed along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've taken some damage, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could rest a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about how they gotta feel, \Ninvading enemy territory, this ain't nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stab
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:26.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Eastern Solid Script!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:29.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:33.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy Egg Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A sneak attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:40.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've already been traced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys should have \Nbeen defeated by Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:43.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Zuzazazazaza...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:50.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I lost my sword, that does \Nnot change the manner of my battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The runes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:54.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:56.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Hades will be angry \Nif we stay defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to all the damage \Nyou guys have done...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...if we accomplish something now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll definitely get promoted \Ninto the 7 Kin of Purgatory-pero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to restore the runes, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:18.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna stay down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seith Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.62,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy? He's super-hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:47.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'cause I've already \NSelf-Strengthened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:51.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought Happy stole that doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a spare, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Mr. Cursey #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,#2?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I haven't missed a beat and I \Nalready stole one of you guys' hairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go freaking out just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:10.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can learn from my past losses at battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change Mr. #2 to be made of iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:20.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, if you want to get back together \Nwith me, you just need to say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My new special move that \NI learned from my loss:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Metallic Rocket Mr. #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge me, Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, such beautiful love \Nbetween brother and sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of girls tell me they \Nwant to be my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am one of the 7 Kin of Purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:55.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will still use my full strength \Nto destroy weaklings like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:58.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... we're Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:15.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Romeo hasn't come back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's tagging along with \NAl and Bisca on a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:22.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They better not have ditched him and \Nstarted makin' out or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got more people than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can't say I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:37.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting more famous, and the number of \Njobs we've got has increased correspondingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at all these requests!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it matters to you, \NMr. I Never Go on a Job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is something to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For I have completed a new dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I name it, the "Dance of Greatest Power!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure. Good job there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Droy... Are you still stuffing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! I can eat all \NI want and stay thin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki, how long has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bunch of long-term jobs in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep pigging out like that, \Nand you're gonna get like Reedus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:12.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui. I'm large because \Nof magic, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Lately you keep \Ngoin' on every job you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:23.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's a wizard's son, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he don't take after \Nhis dad, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring without \NNatsu-nii and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:35.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become like \NNatsu, don't you, Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:39.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But without them, no matter how \Nmany people are in the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Definitely kind of quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:45.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S Class wizards, the strongest \Nteam... Dragon Slayers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're now the top in Fiore, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without them, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, nice and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S Class, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there is some job that only I \Ncan do? That's perfect for {\i1}me{\i0}, up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you choose one of the \Nones you're staring at, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years have you been standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:09.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the S Class Exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how it's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are really great this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why did Wendy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was someone's partner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no... There were only 7 this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting up in years?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgotten who the candidates were again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Natsu-nii can become S Class?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:35.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, I'm gonna become \Nan S Class wizard for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it there, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better become a wizard first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:41.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to get anywhere \Nsearching all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Carla is exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:53.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Split up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're splitting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who designed this crazy ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared... I'm not scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Came up empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all move further on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:41.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a hit, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:46.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't be Grimoire Heart if we didn't \Npay you back tenfold for what you did to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, we will finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a friggin' break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You busted up the exam, hurt my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:02.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You targeted wounded who couldn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who gotta \Npay you back, big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Head to Lisanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The runes are done with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have completed a minimal defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the next step is eliminating these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:41.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're not in the leadership, but you \Ndid manage to injure Gajeel that severely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them attack \Ntogether... It's a real pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:49.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Lisanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to fight a wizard that changes their \Nelement back and forth is to work as a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:13:00.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be a match alone, \Nbut together there's a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an Amaterasu formation...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter and fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:43.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are hit by it\N lose all power in their limbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and it is impossible\N for them to move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you defend against it, your \Nmagic power will be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus... Were you this strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That power was just from one leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And both my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my head, and my entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I attack with all of them at once, we're \Nnot talkin' two or three times stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna try me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the confidence of youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:30.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But youth is not what is needed \Nto walk the path of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Youth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:51.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, a pure soul, will never fall \Nfor your attempts to seduce me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:53.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:57.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's about time to finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:15:00.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will end it quickly in an instant, \Nso that you do not feel pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hot! You burnt my bristle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, marshmallow man! \NTime to take you down a peg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who you callin' a marshmallow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Card Magic, Summoned Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:26.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you another one that's \Nfallen for my manliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a particular \Ntype of girl I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I take all comers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And my attack isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:37.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change Mr. Cursey #2 to electric power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-Strengthen, lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real pain, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not fast enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With my Self-Strengthening, \NI can dodge that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prayer's Fountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton is sucking up the \Nwater, and getting heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-Strengthen, heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:02.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What an exchange... Cana \Nis really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what it takes to be a \Ncandidate in the S Class Wizard Exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss when I have two of \Nyou approaching me so fervently...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's my time to be popular, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this might be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been doing this shtick \Non purpose, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the three of us, we \Ncan handle this somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you can what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to fight me three on one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being confessed to by three \Ngirls at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how popular am I all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But! I am awkward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm a manly man, as you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A serious relationship should be one on one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So which one of you is it \Ngoing to be? Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:51.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were going to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Solid Script: Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Penguin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:07.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you there, Elf-niichan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:20.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the forbidden \Ndouble-Self-Strengthen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My replacement, Mr. Cursey #3!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my hair and his hair, \NI can change bodies at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And on myself, Self-Strengthen with mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:34.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I am impervious to all \Nphysical and secondary attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Runes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:47.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We figured this might happen, so Fried \Nplaced a number around earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:50.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a rune trap that makes it \Nimpossible to use magic. Activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to piling \Non, leave that to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:58.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion on the right and storm on my left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Combine them together for:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Unison Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? My second loss in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we just got \Nanother promotion-pero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:25.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got an even better \Nchance of moving up-pero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're happy because their \Ncomrade got defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a Dark Guild, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot understand how they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's clean them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:47.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little too soon to be bending knee \Nto me after the boasting you just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He got hit by that magic earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world... sure is vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think there'd be monsters \Nlike this in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well, Laxus fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that ends now. You shall now disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...not a member of Fairy Tail any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let yourself be hit by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to get pissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the old man got done in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:15.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:25.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus's lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:49.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My anger... Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:04.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for... the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Electrified?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all of my magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave his magic power to Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ate lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he got sick from it the last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:28.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus... He took that blow \Nwithout any magic power at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how much he wanted to \Ngive Natsu-san his magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... to me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... weaker than Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't about bein' strong or weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it that got hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:52.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be someone with the \Nmark of the guild, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the guild that'll pay him back \Nfor the pain suffered by the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,100 times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fusion of flame and lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thunder-Flame Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:23.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's payback... times 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:59.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder-Flame Dragon? Isn't that acting \Na little bit too cool for you, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.82,0:24:02.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't acting, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.10,0:24:05.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair that I can't \Nhave something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:10.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had lightning powers, Happy, wouldn't \Nyou just be a Flying Lightning Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like, so totally cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:16.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Deepest Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:20.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that Lily, who's scared \Nof lightning, could never handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:22.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, my character's \Nuniqueness is secure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:24.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what you're worried about...
